Oh hey, do you mind if i play in your pool? **Players**: No no, go ahead! We were just playing anyway :) **Me**: Alright, cool :).  (I proceed to take my shirt of and enjoy their pool)

* 10 minutes later

**Me**: *still in pool* So who are all of you guys? **Players**: Hey! We're from Seattle visiting our parents for the weekend. **Me**: Ahh ok cool, what do y'all play? (hoping they say overwatch) **players**: Overwatch mostly when we have time. We don't play ranked anymore though. What about you? **Me**: Ohhhhh nice nice. That sounds super fun :) . You guys should check out this awesome overwatch community on here called u/competitiveoverwatch haha. How old are all of you guys? **players**: We are mostly around 13-14...ish?? and then my sister over there is 18 and on vacation with us too... Why? And what's that subreddit called again? **Me**: Hmmm interesting. Umm no just curious hehe ;)  Anyway thats where i live over there, u/competitiveoverwatch hahaha! It's like a gaming family on reddit where people post about news/advice on overwatch, tips, cool plays like yours, team looking for players stuff, and people even schedule pickup games on discord! Its super cool!! There even was like two or three players this season who made it into overwatch league from that community ^_^ 

*I said it with so much enthusiasm and joy and was hoping maybe they could catch up on time and play with others through discord (and also to make other players aware of that community as well)*

**Players**: Wow that sound amazingggg!!! Is there a discord link or anything like that?! If so please share!!!

Well ladies n gentleman,  as the title suggest they went home today at 6pm. BUT they ended up adding me and we had a quick chat party through discord after that :) :) Its been about an hour now and although they haven't responded after I told them good night.... But still man, im glad as hell that they added me.  Also,  they made like 2 replies each on my thread which gave me more reddit-karma than any of my other posts in last year. Now I know how you guys feel when people keep upvoting stuff :) I also found another kid from NY that added me through that post from a completely different state... Well.... Now i think i should probably go sleep now because Im really exhausted.  My throat hurts and its past 11pm.  Thanks a lot guys <3. Forgive any grammar errors....   Peace out!!! :)
